725623f-a.title: Queens: 73rd Avenue - 183rd Street
725623f-a.text:
73rd Avenue, north side, at 183rd Street, showing the
I. Rapelye farmhouse of 1860. Later owners were: W. J.
Lawrence-1873; Eisman-1891 to 1909.
